<plot>Deep within the bowels of a WWI trench, young brothers James and Charles struggle to stay alive. But when James begins having visions of a light that foretells the deaths of comrades, Charles fears for his sanity and swears him to secrecy. However, the day arrives when James sees the light on Charles, and is forced to take matters into his own hands to change his brother's destiny. But he soon discovers that the future isn't easily manipulated, and must face his own fears to fight fate itself in a race to save his brother's life.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?571027</url></doc>
